何時に起きたの?

10
00:00:19,410 --> 00:00:20,040
Lunch.
お昼

11
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,705
That was the kind of sleep you get when you sleep too much.
あれ、寝過ぎた時の眠りだったじゃん

12
00:00:24,705 --> 00:00:25,360
vice versa.
逆に

13
00:00:25,360 --> 00:00:29,960
I feel more refreshed if I live a relatively regular life.
割と規則正しく生きている方が スッキリする

14
00:00:29,960 --> 00:00:31,380
surely.
確かに

15
00:00:31,380 --> 00:00:34,160
I feel sleepier when I sleep during the day.
昼間寝たりする方が眠たい

16
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:36,860
I brought some alcohol.
酒持ったよ

17
00:00:38,460 --> 00:00:38,800
terrible.
やばい

18
00:00:40,160 --> 00:00:41,520
