やばいマツだ

49
00:04:00,635 --> 00:04:01,860
I need to lose weight.
痩せないと

50
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,645
I'm saying this because summer has already started.
もう夏始まんで言ってる

51
00:04:05,645 --> 00:04:06,740
Seriously dangerous?
マジでやばい?

52
00:04:58,780 --> 00:04:59,500
terrible.
やばい

53
